@model JioCxRcsWrapper.Application.Common.Pagination.PagedResult<JioCxRcsWrapper.Application.Reports.CampaignReportSummary>
@inject JioCxRcsWrapper.Web.Services.PermissionUiService PermissionUi
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Reports";
    var canDownload = await PermissionUi.CanAsync("Reports", "Download");
}

<section class="page-hero report-hero">
    <div>
        <div class="page-eyebrow">Analytics</div>
        <h1>Reports</h1>
        <p>Campaign delivery, failures, and downloadable report exports.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="metric-strip">
    <article class="metric-tile"><span>Total Sent</span><strong>@ViewBag.TotalSent</strong></article>
    <article class="metric-tile"><span>Delivered</span><strong>@ViewBag.Delivered</strong></article>
    <article class="metric-tile"><span>Failed</span><strong>@ViewBag.Failed</strong></article>
    <article class="metric-tile"><span>Campaigns</span><strong>@ViewBag.CampaignCount</strong></article>
</section>

<section class="panel-card mb-4">
    <div class="panel-card-header">
        <div>
            <h2>Filters</h2>
            <p>Filter reports by campaign or client name.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4">
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <label class="form-label">Campaign Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="CampaignName" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["CampaignName"]" placeholder="Filter by campaign..." />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <label class="form-label">Client Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm grid-filter" data-column="ClientName" value="@ViewContext.HttpContext.Request.Query["ClientName"]" placeholder="Filter by client..." />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="panel-card">
    <div class="panel-card-header d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        <div>
            <h2>Campaign Reports</h2>
            <p>Open details or export CSV/PDF for each campaign.</p>
        </div>
        @if (canDownload)
        {
            <button type="button" id="bulk-download-btn" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">Download Selected (CSV)</button>
        }
    </div>
    <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="table panel-table align-middle mb-0">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                @if (canDownload)
                {
                    <th><input type="checkbox" id="select-all-reports" /></th>
                }
                <th>Campaign</th>
                <th>Client</th>
                <th>Sent</th>
                <th>Delivered</th>
                <th>Failed</th>
                <th class="text-end action-cell">Actions</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            @foreach (var report in Model.Items)
            {
                <tr>
                    @if (canDownload)
                    {
                        <td><input type="checkbox" class="report-checkbox" data-id="@report.CampaignId" /></td>
                    }
                    <td class="fw-semibold">@report.CampaignName</td>
                    <td>@report.ClientName</td>
                    <td>@report.TotalSent</td>
                    <td><span class="status-pill status-active">@report.Delivered</span></td>
                    <td><span class="status-pill @(report.Failed > 0 ? "status-failed" : "status-draft")">@report.Failed</span></td>
                    <td class="text-end action-cell">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-end gap-1">
                            <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@report.CampaignId" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">View</a>
                            @if (canDownload)
                            {
                                <a asp-action="ExportCsv" asp-route-id="@report.CampaignId" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">CSV</a>
                                <a asp-action="ExportPdf" asp-route-id="@report.CampaignId" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">PDF</a>
                            }
                            @if (User.IsInRole("Admin"))
                            {
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-info" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#auditModal-@report.CampaignId" onclick="loadTrace(@report.CampaignId)">
                                    Technical
                                </button>
                                
                                <div class="modal fade" id="auditModal-@report.CampaignId" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">
                                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
                                        <div class="modal-content">
                                            <div class="modal-header">
                                                <h5 class="modal-title text-dark">Campaign API Trace - @report.CampaignName</h5>
                                                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="modal-body text-start text-dark">
                                                <p class="small text-muted">Showing the most recent technical trace for this campaign. Full logs available in details.</p>
                                                <div id="trace-content-@report.CampaignId" style="max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto;">
                                                    <div class="text-center py-4">
                                                        <div class="spinner-border spinner-border-sm text-primary" role="status"></div>
                                                        <span class="ms-2 small">Loading trace data...</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            }
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            }
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <partial name="_Pager" model="Model" />
</section>

@section Scripts {
    <script src="~/js/reports.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    <script>
        async function loadTrace(campaignId) {
            const container = document.getElementById('trace-content-' + campaignId);
            try {
                const response = await fetch('/Reports/GetTechnicalTrace?campaignId=' + campaignId);
                if (!response.ok) throw new Error('Trace not found');
                const data = await response.json();
                
                if (data && data.length > 0) {
                    let html = '';
                    data.forEach(log => {
                        html += `<div class="mb-3 border-bottom pb-2">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between small mb-1">
                                <span class="fw-bold text-primary">${log.status}</span>
                                <span class="text-muted">${new Date(log.timestamp).toLocaleString()}</span>
                            </div>
                            <pre class="bg-light p-2 rounded x-small" style="white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all;"><code>${log.requestPayload || 'No payload'}</code></pre>
                            <pre class="bg-light p-2 rounded x-small" style="white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-all;"><code>${log.responseJson || 'No response'}</code></pre>
                        </div>`;
                    });
                    container.innerHTML = html;
                } else {
                    container.innerHTML = '<div class="alert alert-info py-2 small">No API logs found for this campaign.</div>';
                }
            } catch (err) {
                container.innerHTML = '<div class="alert alert-danger py-2 small">Error loading trace: ' + err.message + '</div>';
            }
        }
    </script>
}
